data.description: A quiet homestead featuring a log cabin home on 5 acres in the beautiful North Georgia mountains. The wood burning fireplace can be used to warm the entire home in the winter and you may cool off in your own private pool in the summer. This property has tremendous potential as a private residence, rental property, or weekend retreat. The family room features a stunning rock fireplace with a beamed vaulted ceiling with loft and an open concept kitchen and dining. With three full levels of living space, the upstairs features a master bedroom, full bath and a nice size loft. Step inside from the spacious front porch into the main level which includes the family room, kitchen/dining, full bath and guest bedroom. In the basement you’ll find two more bedrooms, a full bath, a spacious laundry/storage room and an additional flex room. This authentic log cabin exterior was repaired, sealed, stained and re-chinked in 2022. Connected to County water in 2016, septic serviced and clean out in 2021, vinyl lined pool installed in 2015. Firewood shed added in 2022 (enough split firewood there for your first winter!) Pretty lot with mature fruit trees. Easy access off Reinhardt Parkway. Located only a few miles from Reinhardt University and Lake Arrowhead. Close to all the shopping and restaurants offered in Canton and only an hour from Atlanta. No HOA.
